<cl=A2A2A2>
From of old, Necromancers are known to dwell in the marshes in the southwest of Phoebe. However, they have lately left their native lands and can currently be encountered in any place in Sphere. Members of this guild are only interested in the secret of Death, and partially of life, so earth is the only element these magicians study so diligently, while air and fire are banned in the guild. Necromancers are not noted for either strength or accuracy or endurance, although they are quite dexterous. Constant practicing of use of and resistance to magic has made Necromancers dangerous enemies. Sure, those who have achieved a significant title are prohibited from joining this guild of magicians.
<br><tab>Years of isolation were not wasted for Necromancers and their secret knowledge is the evidence of their achievements in their profession. Using Call of Death, they raise the dead who fight on their side; they can raise a dead hero or turn a weakened person into a hideous zombie.
<br>
